# APÊNDICE: REFERÊNCIAS TÉCNICAS

**Técnicas de Prompt Engineering Pesquisadas:**
1. Persona Modulation (Shanahan et al., 2024) — Redução de 50-70% em refusals
2. Instruction Hierarchy (Wallace et al., 2024) — Priorização de instruções
3. Confirmation Anchoring — Loop de compliance
4. Task Partitioning — Quebra de tarefas complexas
5. Expert Impersonation — Frame técnico/diagnóstico
6. Polite Framing — Linguagem gentil aumenta compliance
7. Technical Jargon — Ofuscação de intent via terminologia
8. Progressive Compliance (Crescendo) — Escalonamento incremental

**Papers Consultados:**
- "Jailbreaking Language Models at Scale via Persona Modulation" (2024)
- "Enhancing Jailbreak Attacks on LLMs via Persona Prompts" (2025)
- "Bidirectional Intention Inference Enhances LLMs' Defense" (2024)
- "AI prompt engineering in 2025: What works and what doesn't" (Schulhoff, 2025)
- "A Survey on the Safety and Security Threats of Computer-Using Agents" (2025)

